<div id="_r_bd_" data-testid="collapsible-user-message-content" class="A_HxFq_content"><div class="max-w-full min-w-0 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] whitespace-pre-wrap">1. Bigger Play Button

Right now the page feels like:

Title
Description
Buttons
Stats

A Poki homepage feels like:

TITLE
PLAY NOW
GAME PREVIEW
Rewards
Progress
Shop
Stats

The Play button should dominate the screen.

Think:

30-40% larger
Pulsing animation
More vertical space around it
2. Live Game Preview

Poki games almost always show gameplay immediately.

Replace the giant logo sphere with:

Gameplay GIF
Gameplay video loop
Interactive preview

This alone could double engagement.

3. Character / Mascot

Your page currently has:

🟣 Purple sphere

That's functional but not memorable.

Geometry Dash has cubes.
Brawl Stars has characters.
Subway Surfers has Jake.

Shift Panic needs:

Main orb with eyes
Animated face
Unlockable expressions

Something players remember.

4. Coins Need More Importance

Right now coins are hidden in the right panel.

Copy Brawl Stars:

Coin counter at top
Gem/premium currency
Daily reward notification

Make progression impossible to miss.

5. Daily Challenge Should Be Huge

Current:

Small card bottom left.

Poki-level:

🔥 DAILY CHALLENGE
Survive 60 seconds
Reward: 25 coins
[ PLAY NOW ]

with glowing borders.

6. Add Achievement Badges

Right side panel could become:

🏆 Panic Rookie
⭐ First Win
⚡ 10,000 Score
💰 Coin Collector

People love visible progress.

7. Search These UI Categories

On Game UI Database search:

Main Menu
Home Screen
Lobby
Progression
Battle Pass
Daily Rewards
Store
Player Profile

Those are the screens most relevant to your homepage.

If I were rebuilding Shift Panic today, I'd copy the layout philosophy of:

Brawl Stars (best overall)
Stumble Guys
Geometry Dash
Subway Surfers make a bunch of prompts in order for me to use to get a really really good homepage with 0 bugs</div></div><button type="button" aria-controls="_r_bd_" aria-expanded="false" class="A_HxFq_toggleControl select-none" data-testid="collapsible-user-message-toggle"><span class="A_HxFq_showMoreLabel">Show more</span><span class="A_HxFq_showLessLabel">Show less</span><div class="A_HxFq_toggleIconWrapper motion-safe:transition-transform motion-safe:duration-150"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" class="A_HxFq_toggleIcon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ba3792" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-cen