<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="11270" data-end="11982"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Add 3 small professional feature cards below or beside the main homepage hero area.</span><br><br><span>Purpose:</span><br><span>Make Shift Panic feel like a complete game and explain why the player should click.</span><br><br><span>Cards:</span><br><span>1. “Dodge the Forbidden Color”</span><br><span>   - mini icon of forbidden color block</span><br><span>   - short text: “The danger color keeps changing.”</span><br><span>2. “Build Combos”</span><br><span>   - mini combo meter icon</span><br><span>   - short text: “Near misses and survival streaks boost your score.”</span><br><span>3. “Unlock Rewards”</span><br><span>   - mini coin/skin icon</span><br><span>   - short text: “Earn coins, skins, abilities, and progress rewards.”</span><br><br><span>Style:</span><br><span>- Glass cards</span><br><span>- Colorful icons</span><br><span>- Hover lift animation</span><br><span>- No huge paragraphs</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Cards fit cleanly.</span><br><span>- No broken icons.</span><br><span>- Text is readable.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
