n><br><span>   - hover state</span><br><span>   - active/click state</span><br><span>4. Disable or mark unfinished modes clearly if they are not production-ready, but do not remove them.</span><br><span>5. If Multiplayer has bugs, label “Beta” instead of pretending it is perfect.</span><br><span>6. Keep all click handlers working.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Every button opens the correct screen/modal.</span><br><span>- No dead buttons.</span><br><span>- Returning home from each screen works.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
