<h1 data-section-id="1ykt5jr" data-start="13639" data-end="13681">PROMPT 12 — Add Better Microinteractions</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="13683" data-end="14318"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Add professional microinteractions to the homepage.</span><br><br><span>Implement:</span><br><span>1. Buttons should scale slightly on hover and depress on click.</span><br><span>2. Cards should have subtle hover glow.</span><br><span>3. Coin count should sparkle lightly.</span><br><span>4. Daily challenge card should have a slow animated shine.</span><br><span>5. The mascot should react when hovering over Play.</span><br><span>6. The Play button should pulse gently, not aggressively.</span><br><span>7. Add sound toggle compatibility if sound exists, but do not force new sound.</span><br><br><span>Important:</span><br><span>Animations must be lightweight. Do not create memory leaks with repeated setIntervals.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Hover effects work.</span><br><span>- No lag.</span><br><span>- No console errors.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="14320" data-end="14323">
<h1 data-section-id="rqkumg" data-start="14325" data-end="14363">PROMPT 13 — Game Over Screen Upgrade</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="14365" data-end="15333"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Upgrade the Endless Mode Game Over screen to feel more rewarding and addictive.</span><br><br><span>Current problem:</span><br><span>The current Game Over card is functional but not exciting enough. It should make players want to retry.</span><br><br><span>Implement:</span><br><span>1. Add stronger hierarchy:</span><br><span>   - Big result message</span><br><span>   - Score</span><br><span>   - Time survived</span><br><span>   - Coins earned</span><br><span>   - Best comparison</span><br><span>   - Combo</span><br><span>2. Add dynamic message based on performance:</span><br><span>   - under 10 sec: “Warming up.”</span><br><span>   - near best: “So close!”</span><br><span>   - new best: “NEW BEST!”</span><br><span>3. Add progress reward preview:</span><br><span>   - lifetime score progress</span><br><span>   - next reward</span><br><span>4. Make Play Again the biggest button.</span><br><span>5. Add secondary buttons:</span><br><span>   - Home</span><br><span>   - Shop</span><br><span>   - Leaderboard</span><br><span>   - Copy Score</span><br><span>6. Add small celebration particles for new best or reward unlocked.</span><br><br><span>Do not:</span><br><span>- Change scoring logic unless there is a bug.</span><br><span>- Award duplicate coins.</span><br><span>- Reset progress.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Play Again works.</span><br><span>- Home works.</span><br><span>- Coins are awarded exactly once.</span><br><span>- New best displays correctly.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="15335" data-end="15338">
<h1 data-section-id="1whbbfl" data-start="15340" data-end="15394">PROMPT 14 — Shop Visual Polish Without Breaking Data</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="15396" data-end="16358"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Polish the Shop UI while preserving all current purchase/unlock/equip logic.</span><br><br><span>Current problem:</span><br><span>The shop is functional but some tabs look inconsistent, and the visual quality is not Poki-level.</span><br><br><span>Implement:</span><br><span>1. Make tab navigation cleaner and more game-like.</span><br><span>2. Make cards more colorful by rarity:</span><br><span>   - Common: simple purple/blue</span><br><span>   - Rare: blue/cyan</span><br><span>   - Epic: orange/purple</span><br><span>   - Legendary: gold/purple</span><br><span>   - Mythic: teal/green</span><br><span>3. Improve selected item preview panel.</span><br><span>4. Ensure all powerup/ability icons render without weird white/checker backgrounds.</span><br><span>5. Use transparent PNGs properly if available.</span><br><span>6. Add fallback icon styling if image fails.</span><br><span>7. Keep all prices, owned states, locked states, equipped states, and progress requirements intact.</span><br><span>8. Fix large empty boxes or misaligned preview areas.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Skins tab works.</span><br><span>- Abilities tab works.</span><br><span>- Powerups tab works.</span><br><span>- Challenges tab works.</span><br><span>- Progress tab works.</span><br><span>- No user progress is lost.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="16360" data-end="16363">
<h1 data-section-id="14mzgbc" data-start="16365" data-end="16411">PROMPT 15 — Panic Quest Entry Card From Home</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="16413" data-end="17147"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Improve how Panic Quest is advertised from the homepage.</span><br><br><span>Current problem:</span><br><span>Panic Quest is just a button. It should feel like a major game mode.</span><br><br><span>Implement:</span><br><span>1. Add a compact Panic Quest preview card near the main buttons.</span><br><span>2. Show:</span><br><span>   - current level/progress if available</span><br><span>   - stars earned</span><br><span>   - next reward</span><br><span>   - “Continue Quest” or “Start Quest”</span><br><span>3. Add a glowing blue/purple adventure style.</span><br><span>4. If Panic Quest is currently broken, do not hide the issue. Fix click routing and ensure it opens.</span><br><span>5. Preserve all existing Panic Quest progress.</span><br><span>6. If the user is on level 3, they should still be on level 3 after changes.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Panic Quest button opens Panic Quest.</span><br><span>- Progress is preserved.</span><br><span>- Returning home works.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="17149" data-end="17152">
<h1 data-section-id="idbwz4" data-start="17154" data-end="17186">PROMPT 16 — Homepage Bug Audit</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="17188" data-end="18071"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Perform a targeted homepage bug audit and fix issues introduced by previous UI changes.</span><br><br><span>Check and fix:</span><br><span>1. Duplicate event listeners on buttons.</span><br><span>2. Buttons that visually exist but do not click.</span><br><span>3. Elements appearing off-screen.</span><br><span>4. Scroll issues on desktop.</span><br><span>5. Content hidden behind fixed headers/footers.</span><br><span>6. Settings button overlapping UI.</span><br><span>7. Background animation memory leaks.</span><br><span>8. localStorage read/write errors.</span><br><span>9. Firebase errors that break homepage load.</span><br><span>10. Console errors.</span><br><span>11. Route/menu state getting stuck.</span><br><span>12. Homepage not resetting correctly after returning from game/game over/shop.</span><br><br><span>Do not redesign new features in this prompt. Focus on stability.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Hard refresh homepage.</span><br><span>- Open Endless, return Home.</span><br><span>- Open Shop, close.</span><br><span>- Open Leaderboard, close.</span><br><span>- Open Help, close.</span><br><span>- Open Panic Quest, return Home.</span><br><span>- No console errors.</span><br><span>- No lost progress.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="18073" data-end="18076">
<h1 data-section-id="1bzarzu" data-start="18078" data-end="18128">PROMPT 17 — Make Homepage Feel Like a Game Lobby</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="18130" data-end="18889"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Transform the homepage into a polished “game lobby” experience.</span><br><br><span>Add these lobby-like features:</span><br><span>1. Top currency/status strip:</span><br><span>   - coins</span><br><span>   - best score</span><br><span>   - rank</span><br><span>   - settings</span><br><span>2. Center hero:</span><br><span>   - mascot/player preview</span><br><span>   - title</span><br><span>   - Play button</span><br><span>3. Side widgets:</span><br><span>   - Daily challenge</span><br><span>   - Quest progress</span><br><span>   - Next unlock</span><br><span>4. Bottom nav:</span><br><span>   - Shop</span><br><span>   - Leaderboard</span><br><span>   - Multiplayer</span><br><span>   - Help</span><br><span>5. Add small notification badges:</span><br><span>   - NEW on Panic Quest</span><br><span>   - CLAIM if daily reward is claimable</span><br><span>   - SHOP if unlock available</span><br><span>6. Ensure badges are real and not misleading.</span><br><br><span>Style:</span><br><span>Colorful, bold, arcade-like, readable, polished.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Layout looks intentional.</span><br><span>- No fake notifications unless state supports it.</span><br><span>- Main play path is obvious.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
