<h1 data-section-id="11g5r2p" data-start="19580" data-end="19612">PROMPT 19 — Add Safe Fallbacks</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="19614" data-end="20238"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Add safety fallbacks so the homepage never appears broken or empty.</span><br><br><span>Implement:</span><br><span>1. If saved stats fail to load, show safe defaults but do not overwrite stored data.</span><br><span>2. If an icon/image fails, show a styled CSS fallback.</span><br><span>3. If Firebase fails, homepage still loads.</span><br><span>4. If preview animation fails, homepage still loads.</span><br><span>5. If a button target is unavailable, show a small friendly error toast instead of black screen.</span><br><span>6. Add console warnings for recoverable failures, but no uncaught exceptions.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance test:</span><br><span>- Simulate missing image path if possible.</span><br><span>- Homepage still loads.</span><br><span>- No black screen.</span><br><span>- No data reset.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="20240" data-end="20243">
<h1 data-section-id="b05ro0" data-start="20245" data-end="20283">PROMPT 20 — Final QA Checklist + Fix</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="20285" data-end="21018"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Run a final QA pass on the homepage and fix anything broken.</span><br><br><span>Test these flows:</span><br><span>1. Hard refresh at shiftpanic.com.</span><br><span>2. Click Play Endless.</span><br><span>3. Move player.</span><br><span>4. Die.</span><br><span>5. Click Play Again.</span><br><span>6. Return Home.</span><br><span>7. Click Panic Quest.</span><br><span>8. Return Home.</span><br><span>9. Open Shop.</span><br><span>10. Switch Shop tabs: Skins, Abilities, Powerups, Challenges, Progress.</span><br><span>11. Close Shop.</span><br><span>12. Open Leaderboard.</span><br><span>13. Open Help.</span><br><span>14. Open Settings.</span><br><span>15. Refresh again and verify progress remains.</span><br><br><span>Fix any issues found.</span><br><br><span>Do not add major new features in this prompt. Only fix and polish.</span><br><br><span>Acceptance criteria:</span><br><span>- No black screens.</span><br><span>- No frozen player.</span><br><span>- No missing buttons.</span><br><span>- No console errors.</span><br><span>- No progress loss.</span><br><span>- Homepage looks polished, colorful, and Poki-ready on desktop.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="21020" data-end="21023">
<h2 data-section-id="12pi6gj" data-start="21025" data-end="21052">My honest recommendation</h2>
<p data-start="21054" data-end="21158">Do <strong data-start="21057" data-end="21064">not</strong> queue all 20 overnight this time unless Copilot has been stable. For your situation, do this:</p>
<p data-start="21160" data-end="21196">First queue <strong data-start="21172" data-end="21195">1, 2, 7, 16, 19, 20</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="21198" data-end="21411" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">That gives you the biggest homepage improvement while reducing the chance Copilot breaks the game again. Then test. After that, queue the creative ones like mascot, live preview, daily challenge, and lobby polish.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-