ve min-w-0 overflow-hidden rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="max-w-full min-w-0 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] whitespace-pre-wrap">is this a poki level homepage</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Share prompt" data-testid="share-prompt-link-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#630ca2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="request-69cdbfd2-9e14-832b-a560-80bc2114dc10-4" data-is-intersecting="true" style="--last-known-height: 72px;"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-69cdbfd2-9e14-832b-a560-80bc2114dc10-4" data-turn-id-container="request-69cdbfd2-9e14-832b-a560-80bc2114dc10-4" data-testid="conversation-turn-586" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary flex items-center gap-0.5 text-start dark:text-(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)">Thought for a few seconds<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="68f970b2-928d-475e-a1b8-a0457a4f1549" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="159">Yes — <strong data-start="6" data-end="63">the direction is much closer to a Poki-level homepage</strong>, but I would not call it “ready” yet unless it is implemented cleanly inside your real game UI.</p>
<p data-start="161" data-end="202">A Poki-level homepage needs three things:</p>
<ol data-start="204" data-end="458">
<li data-section-id="sfuha6" data-start="204" data-end="293">
<p data-start="207" data-end="293"><strong data-start="207" data-end="226">Instant clarity</strong>: the player immediately understands “press play and dodge colors.”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ctwe83" data-start="294" data-end="370">
<p data-start="297" data-end="370"><strong data-start="297" data-end="316">Big visual hook</strong>: mascot, action, danger blocks, coins, reward energy.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="jl1asq" data-start="371" data-end="458">
<p data-start="374" data-end="458"><strong data-start="374" data-end="390">Clean layout</strong>: not too much text, no clutter, no weird spacing, no broken panels.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="460" data-end="755">The image is good as a <strong data-start="483" data-end="524">homepage concept / hero art direction</strong>, not necessarily as the full UI by itself. You should use it as inspiration or as a background/hero image, then make Copilot build the actual buttons, stats, daily challenge, shop, and leaderboard on top of it using real HTML/CSS.</p>
<p data-start="757" data-end="775">Save the image as:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="777" data-end="813"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>shiftpanic-home-hero.png</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="815" data-end="825">Put it in:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="827" data-end="878"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>/public/assets/shiftpanic-home-hero.png</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="880" data-end="910">Then give Copilot this prompt:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="912" data-end="4388"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>You are improving the Shift Panic homepage to be Poki-ready. Use the new image asset located at /public/assets/shiftpanic-home-hero.png as the main homepage hero artwork/background inspiration.</span><br><br><span>IMPORTANT:</span><br><span>- Do not delete player progress.</span><br><span>- Do not reset coins, best score, lifetime score, skins, achievements, challenges, or any localStorage/Firebase progress.</span><br><span>- Do not break Endless mode, Panic Quest, Shop, Leaderboard, Multiplayer, or Help buttons.</span><br><span>- Preserve all existing game logic. This task is UI-only unless a bug is found.</span><br><br><span>Goal:</span><br><span>Make the desktop homepage look like a polished Poki/browser arcade game homepage. The current homepage has too much text, too much empty purple space, and not enough visual excitement. Redesign it to feel colorful, professional, clickable, and instantly understandable.</span><br><br><span>Homepage layout requirements:</span><br><span>1. Full-screen arcade lobby layout.</span><br><span>2. Main center hero area with:</span><br><span>   - Large Shift Panic logo/title.</span><br><span>   - Main mascot/orb character visible.</span><br><span>   - Short tagline only: “Dodge the forbidden color. Survive the panic.”</span><br><span>   - Huge primary PLAY NOW / PLAY ENDLESS button.</span><br><span>   - Secondary PANIC QUEST button.</span><br><span>3. The Play button must be the biggest interaction on the page:</span><br><span>   - 30–40% larger than secondary buttons.</span><br><span>   - Bright gradient.</span><br><span>   - Soft glow.</span><br><span>   - Hover scale effect.</span><br><span>   - Very obvious click target.</span><br><span>4. Add a small live preview / hero art panel using shiftpanic-home-hero.png:</span><br><span>   - Use it either as a right-side gameplay preview card or as a softened background image inside the hero panel.</span><br><span>   - Do not let it make text unreadable.</span><br><span>   - Add dark overlay if needed.</span><br><span>5. Reduce text:</span><br><span>   - Remove long paragraphs like “Why players love Shift Panic.”</span><br><span>   - Replace with 3 small pill badges only:</span><br><span>     “Fast reflexes”</span><br><span>     “Color switching”</span><br><span>     “Unlock skins”</span><br><span>6. Add a top HUD bar:</span><br><span>   - Left: player rank/title.</span><br><span>   - Right: coin counter and settings button.</span><br><span>   - Make it clean and game-like.</span><br><span>7. Add right-side progression panel:</span><br><span>   - Best score</span><br><span>   - Coins</span><br><span>   - Lifetime score progress</span><br><span>   - Rank</span><br><span>   - 3–5 achievement badges</span><br><span>8. Add Daily Challenge as a big, colorful card:</span><br><span>   - Title: “Daily Challenge”</span><br><span>   - Objective</span><br><span>   - Reward</span><br><span>   - Small “Play” button</span><br><span>   - Make it visually important, not tiny.</span><br><span>9. Background:</span><br><span>   - Keep purple/neon identity.</span><br><span>   - Add more color through glowing blocks, particles, coins, and gradients.</span><br><span>   - Avoid flat black panels.</span><br><span>10. Visual polish:</span><br><span>   - Rounded cards.</span><br><span>   - Consistent spacing.</span><br><span>   - High contrast text.</span><br><span>   - Strong button states.</span><br><span>   - Smooth hover animations.</span><br><span>   - No overlapping elements.</span><br><span>   - No giant blank areas.</span><br><span>11. Desktop-first:</span><br><span>   - Optimize for 1366x768 and 1920x1080.</span><br><span>   - The whole main homepage should fit without requiring the player to scroll just to find Play.</span><br><span>   - If scrolling exists, it should be for extra content only, not core navigation.</span><br><br><span>Implementation details:</span><br><span>- Search the codebase for the homepage/menu component and update only the relevant CSS/JS/HTML.</span><br><span>- Keep all button IDs, click handlers, and routing functions working.</span><br><span>- After changes, manually verify:</span><br><span>  1. Play Endless opens Endless mode.</span><br><span>  2. Panic Quest opens the level/challenge screen.</span><br><span>  3. Shop opens.</span><br><span>  4. Leaderboard opens.</span><br><span>  5. Help opens.</span><br><span>  6. Settings opens.</span><br><span>  7. Coins/progress still display correctly.</span><br><span>  8. No console errors.</span><br><span>  9. The page looks good at 1366x768 and 1920x1080.</span><br><br><span>Do not stop after making cosmetic changes. Actually test the click handlers and fix anything broken before finishing.</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="4390" data-end="4664" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">My honest take: <strong data-start="4406" data-end="4512">your current real homepage is getting better, but it still feels like a developer UI with game colors.</strong> To reach Poki level, you need one strong visual centerpiece, fewer words, and a huge obvious Play button. This prompt should push it in that direction.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://w