lex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary flex items-center gap-0.5 text-start dark:text-(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)">Thought for 5s<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="fd472a20-e67c-4857-895a-38a75f3ab12f" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-turn-start-message="true" tabindex="0"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="141">Do <strong data-start="3" data-end="10">not</strong> just copy/paste the image into the code. That usually causes bugs, huge messy base64 code, slow loading, and Copilot may break it.</p>
<p data-start="143" data-end="159">Do this instead:</p>
<ol data-start="161" data-end="236">
<li data-section-id="r7paxn" data-start="161" data-end="214">
<p data-start="164" data-end="214"><strong data-start="164" data-end="196">Download/save the image file</strong> to your computer.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="es89tc" data-start="215" data-end="236">
<p data-start="218" data-end="236">Rename it exactly:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="238" data-end="274"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>shiftpanic-home-hero.png</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="3" data-start="276" data-end="307">
<li data-section-id="nqvbuf" data-start="276" data-end="307">
<p data-start="279" data-end="307">Put it in your project here:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="309" data-end="359"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>public/assets/shiftpanic-home-hero.png</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="361" data-end="420">If there is no <code data-start="376" data-end="384">assets</code> folder, create one inside <code data-start="411" data-end="419">public</code>.</p>
<p data-start="422" data-end="440">Then tell Copilot:</p>
