C_oled-mode.png\",\"office_label\":\"New York City\",\"starter_prompt\":\"What is Grand Central Food Fair 2026, and what happens at the Midtown East street fair?\",\"developer_instructions\":\"The user clicked a ChatGPT homepage doodle. Do not ask them to upload or show the doodle. Concisely explain the event behind the doodle with concrete details: what date \u0026 time the event is in bold, who it centers on or brings together, what the event is, where it happens, why it matters, and how the doodle's visual details connect to that story. Keep the event explanation to at most 1-2 short paragraphs. Make sure you use the right tense for when the event is happening. Use the map widget to ground your answer in the doodle's New York City context. If you can identify the most relevant venue, neighborhood, or event location, include it on the map while you explain the doodle. Answer the user's visible prompt using this doodle context:\",\"event_title\":\"Grand Central Food Fair 2026\",\"dark_image_url\":\"https://persistent.oaistatic.com/chatgpt/doodles/2026-05-21-to-2026-05-24-manual-dark-oled-review/may-21/nyc/may-21_NYC_dark-mode.png\"},\"sf\":{\"dark_image_url\":\"https://persistent.oaistatic.com/chatgpt/doodles/2026-05-21-to-2026-05-24-manual-dark-oled-review/may-21/sf/may-21_SF_dark-mode.png\",\"oled_image_url\":\"https://persistent.oaistatic.com/chatgpt/doodles/2026-05-21-to-2026-05-24-manual-dark-oled-review/may-21/sf/may-21_SF_oled-mode.png\",\"starter_question\":\"Can you explain the context behind this ChatGPT homepage doodle? It was created for AAPI Heritage Month SF Downtown Block Party ft. Jai Wolf \u0026 Friends in San Francisco, using downtown block-party energy, AAPI celebration, music/DJ set, street-festival atmosphere. What event is it referencing, and how do those details tell the story?\",\"developer_instructions\":\"The user clicked a ChatGPT homepage doodle. Do not ask them to upload or show the doodle. Concisely explain the event behind the doodle with concrete details: what date \u0026 time the event is in bold, who it centers on or brings together, what the event is, where it happens, why it matters, and how the doodle's visual details connect to that story. Keep the event explanation to at most 1-2 short paragraphs. Make sure you use the right tense for when the event is happening. Use the map widget to ground your answer in the doodle's San Francisco context. If you can identify the most relevant venue, neighborhood, or event location, include it on the map while you explain the doodle. Answer the user's visible prompt using this doodle context:\",\"office_label\":\"San Francisco\",\"light_image_url\":\"https://persistent.oaistatic.com/chatgpt/doodles/2026-05-21-to-2026-05-24-manual-dark-oled-review/may-21/sf/may-21_SF_light-mode.png\",\"event_title\":\"AAPI Heritage Month SF Downtown Block Party ft. Jai Wolf \u0026 Friends\",\"starter_prompt\":\"What is AAPI Heritage Month SF Downtown Block Party ft. Jai Wolf \u0026 Friends, and what happens at the downtown block party?\"}}},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"2076138851\":{\"name\":\"2076138851\",\"rule_id\":\"3QigorHh71tggge0e0kFbD\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"max_concurrency\":20},\"is_device_based\":false,\"group_name\":\"20\",\"is_experiment_active\":true,\"is_user_in_experiment\":true},\"2850107578\":{\"name\":\"2850107578\",\"rule_id\":\"7nxmtzMrThjQ6ucoe2XHVB:100.00:19-7nxmty7pqZalN4EsCV24Cz\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"onboarding\":{\"screen_personalization_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/bazaar/onboarding/personalization_en.png\",\"screen_transparency_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/bazaar/onboarding/controls_en.png\",\"card_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/onboarding/onboarding-example-1.png\",\"screen_trust_image_url\":\"https://cdn.openai.com/chatgpt/clients/bazaar/onboarding/trusted_en.png\",\"scree